ntirheumatic drugs (DMARDs), or potent immunosuppressants (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/38913/', '', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Baricitinib, Tofacitinib, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, Emapalumab, Sutimlimab, More', 1767369485);
